      "text": "そんなことまだ誰にも言われていないだろう\nいい加減準備しないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now you’re just making things up.\nYou need to get ready for the live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
