      "text": "くっ……{user}さんまで\n私を空気だと仰りたいの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? {user}-san? Even you’re saying that\nI have no presence?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.74104289213815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 39.44104289213815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ふっ！　ゆっ！　かっ！　いっ！\nですわっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That. Is. So.\nOffensive!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.13326831431614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 42.64104289213814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……一体どうしたっていうんだ？\n本番前だからナーバスになっているのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What on earth are you saying?\nAre you getting nervous before the show?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 49.03042269921767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "これですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s about this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.03042269921767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 52.13333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "さっきスマホで\n「月のテンペスト」を軽く検索してみましたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just did a quick search\nfor “Moon Tempest” on my phone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 57.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "本番前にそういうものは\n見ない方がいいと言っただろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Didn’t I tell you not to\ndo that kind of thing before a show?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、軽くですわよ！\nか・る・く！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why it was just a quick search!\nJust! Quick!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 64.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
