      "text": "それで『月のテンペスト　可愛い』とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I looked for “Moon Tempest‚ cute‚”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "『成宮すず　美人』とかで検索したんですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Suzu Narumiya‚ beauty”‚ that kind of thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 72.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、いい評判しか出ないはず\n……と思ったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought I’d only get hits saying nice things‚\nbut instead…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "嫌なことが書いてあったから落ち込んでたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re feeling down because someone wrote something you didn’t like?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "違いますわ。画面をよくご覧なさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not it. Take a good look at this screen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 84.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なになに……『琴乃ちゃんキレイ！　俺の推し決定』\n『渚ちゃん可愛い！　ライブ絶対行く』……か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s this… “Kotono-chan is so pretty! She’s totally my favorite.”\n“Nagisa-chan is cute! I’m going to her show for sure”… and so on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "みんないい反応じゃないか\nどうしてこれを読んで落ち込んだんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aren’t those all good reactions?\nWhy does reading them depress you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 100.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "だって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "どこにも、私のことが書いてないんですのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "nobody wrote anything about ME!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
